Description: CPU Governor Control Daemon
 A lightweight D-Bus system service that provides authorized access
 to CPU frequency scaling governor settings via Polkit.
 .
 This daemon is required by the CPUGov GUI application (available as
 a Flatpak from Flathub) to change CPU governors with proper
 privilege management.
